## Development

To set up this plugin locally, first checkout the code. Then create a new virtual environment:

    cd datasette-basemap
    python3 -mvenv venv
    source venv/bin/activate

Or if you are using `pipenv`:

    pipenv shell

Now install the dependencies and tests:

    pip install -e '.[test]'

To run the tests:

    pytest


